goals.active: Escort the Pact tanks to the Cathedral of Zephyrs.
goals.complete: As part of the Pact's march on Orr, I led a squad charged with clearing a path for our heavy mobile artillery. We reached our destination, but lost a brave sylvari named Tegwen, who stayed behind to ensure our mission was successful. We mourned our loss, but prepared to move on to our next objective so our tanks could be put to good use.
